reviewText: A bad and old movie, a complete waste of money! Please don't be cheated for the description of the movie.
It was a good idea that failed because of excessive reliance on Doris Wishman movie trailers.  There was a whole universe of better product available to them.  Really disappointing execution.
I did not like this DVD. I think I was not wright win I saw the cover and was looking for a movie about the Goddess.

The title and cover art of this DVD titillated my hopes, but is is basically just a string of bad movie trailers interspersed with some bad comedy; and it does end (thankfully) at around the 82-minute mark.
